    End If

    Note: Pop elements in reverse order (LIFO returns last-pushed
    Note: first), storing each at its source-order offset.
    Let depth be proc lowering_result_depth from LCtx with ctx
    Let to_pop be element_count
    If to_pop is greater than depth:
