Note: ============================================================

@Reasoning
HIR_TUPLE_LITERAL post: lowers a tuple literal (a, b, c) to an
alloca for the tuple plus a sequence of field stores at the per-
field offsets. Field offsets are computed from the per-element
types in source order; for the foundation pipeline we use 8-byte
slots uniformly because MIR types are not yet layout-aware.
@End Reasoning

